I'm not trying to be a pain or anything. It's just that I don't hunt level 1 mobs much (OK, at all <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) so the damage I do in a PA against them doesn't tell me much. <p><br><TABLE bgColor=black border=0 cellPadding=0 cellSpacing=0 width=500> <TR><TD><IMG src="http://nemus.freewebspace.com/inf_sig.jpg"></TD></TR></TABLE></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uakak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Akak</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/4/02 5:28:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: but...</span><hr size=1> True, the max damage does go up a bit when you add CS.   I did a simple test on Level 1 grays after leveling but before specing CS.  It went something like:<br>
<br>
At Level 21 with 18 CS:  Backstab II on 10 wolf pups:  238 every time(or something like that)<br>
<br>
At Levl 21 with 19 CS:  Backstab II on 10 wolf pups:  240 every time.  <br>
<br>
So a full point of spec got me 0.8% increase in MAX damage.  Obviously, my increase in average damage on blue, yellow, red or purple mobs would be much lower. <br>
<br>
so an increase of 6% in level (skill 18 to 19) gives you an increase of 0.8% maximum damage on lowest grays.  You can approximate this to be an increase of about 0.4% in average damage.<br>
<br>
If that's Mythic's idea of damage scaling with skill, I think those points would be better used in thrust or envenom. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showMessage?topicID=1580.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showMessage?topicID=1566.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=1577.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.threadControl?topicID=1577.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1577.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1577.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselab